data.text:
@ShurimanTrash Jet, however, was now biding his time. He kept a safe distance from the robo and its pilot, simply veering his Type-J from side to side with an almost hypnotic rhythm, like the flicking of a serpent's tail as it eyes its prey.

"Luck's got nothing to do with it," he cawed, ...

users.description: The universe's fastest speed demon and thrill-seeker, as well as proud leader of the Babylon Rogues. My reputation speaks for itself. ((RP)) ((Sonicverse/MV))
users.name: Jet the Hawk
